A multi-choice question</p></div>
<div class="iDevice emphasis0">
<div id="2_1" style="display:block"><p>In eXe teachers can create multi-choice questions with the following features:</p> <ul>   <li>the option of including a hint for learners<br />   </li>   <li>customised feedback for the correct answer</li>   <li>customised feedback for the incorrect alternatives</li> </ul> The multi-choice feature is not intended to replace the assessment tools in Moodle. They are best used as formative assessment interactions for learners interacting with new content to be learned. Have a look at the example below.</div></div>
