<span class="iDeviceTitle">The end of transmission pedagogy</span><br/>
<div class="iDevice_inner">
<p> Many educators are on a crusade to rid the world of transmission pedagogy, Yet eXe is developing another content authoring tool!</p><p><span style="font-style: italic">With this paradox in mind, what course of action do you recommend for the eXe project?</span>  <br /> </p> &nbsp;&nbsp;
